Y leverir bos '''Dolly Pentreath''', po '''Dorothy Pentreath''' (besydhyes 1692, merwys mis Kevardhu 1777) o an diwettha [[Kernewek|Kerneweger]] genesik ha freth, kyns [[Dasserghyans Kernewek|dasserghyans an yeth]] yn 1904. Kyn y's godhvedhir avel diwettha kowser unyethek an taves  - an diwettha person na gewsi marnas Kernewek, heb Sowsnek - hy derivas hy honan a gontradi hemma.

